These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, australian, indonesian, indian
1. the australian is between the indonesian and the indian##2
2. the australian is on the left of the indonesian##1
3. the french is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Nationality   | french | indian | australian | indonesian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
City: marseilles, hamburg, boston, rome
1. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the person traveling to rome is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person traveling to marseilles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| City   | hamburg | rome | marseilles | boston |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
